Recording artiste Paul Okoye aka Rudeboy has spoken about what he does when eating chicken. Explaining his eating habit, the Okoye twin explained that he throws caution to the wind when eating chicken especially when it has to do with the bones.   Fuji music not for touts, says stakeholders     Davido offers N20m to 20 business startups on Friday     Most dangerous thing about Nigeria, by Simi   The “Reason with Me” singer appealed to persons who may happen to him crushing chicken bones in public to resist the urge to judge him. “If you see me crushing chicken bone in the public, pls don’t mind me…. I no get level for that side,” he said.